        symbol {
            bindings = <
     &kp PIPE         &none  &kp        &kp    &kp PLUS     &kp SLASH  &kp DOLLAR  &kp LEFT_BRACKET      &kp RIGHT_BRACKET      &kp SEMICOLON
     &kp EXCLAMATION  &none  &kp SLASH  &none  &kp EQUAL    &kp ASTRK  &none       &kp LEFT_PARENTHESIS  &kp RIGHT_PARENTHESIS  &kp APOS
&kp  &kp UNDERSCORE   &none  &kp        &kp    &kp MINUS    &kp        &kp         &kp COMMA             &kp PERIOD             &kp            &kp
                             &kp        &kp    &kp          &kp        &kp         &kp
            >;
